For the ratio 1:2
Calculations:
Power <= 1mW
Vdd = 1.8V
Itotal = power/Vdd = 1mW/1.8 = 55.5mA
ID= Itotal/3 = 0.185mA.
1:2 ratio = 0.185mA : 0.37mA.
